1. Download the latest pocketsphinx version (minimum 0.8)

2. Replace the original `src/programs/continous.c` with the modified version `speech_recognition/fatpocketsphinx/modified_continous.c`

3. Compile it and copy the `continous` binary to `speech_recognition/fatpocketsphinx/fatpocketsphinx_continous` (or create a symlink)


